      • onPmtEntry

        public ElementaryStreamReader onPmtEntry(int pid,
                                         int streamType,
                                         ElementaryStreamReader.EsInfo esInfo,
                                         ExtractorOutput output)
        Description copied from interface: ElementaryStreamReader.Factory
        Returns an ElementaryStreamReader for a given PMT entry. May return null if the stream type is not supported or if the stream already has a reader assigned to it.
        Specified by:
        onPmtEntry in interface ElementaryStreamReader.Factory
        Parameters:
        pid - The pid for the PMT entry.
        streamType - One of the TsExtractor.TS_STREAM_TYPE_* constants defining the type of the stream.
        esInfo - The descriptor information linked to the elementary stream.
        output - The ExtractorOutput that provides the TrackOutputs for the created readers.
        Returns:
        An ElementaryStreamReader for the elementary streams carried by the provided pid. null if the stream is not supported or if it should be ignored.
